633,439,Workorder,Examine the patterns of alerts followed by corrective work orders for asset CWC04009 to enhance predictive maintenance for the remainder of its operational life.,Prediction,False,"Identify ALERT → CM WORK_ORDER pairs for CWC04009, measure lead-lag intervals, and summarise patterns that can inform proactive scheduling.",predictive,Equipment,Source: Maintenance operations; Non-deterministic query allowing multiple valid responses; Category: Prediction,paraphrase,,,2025-09-27T10:32:40
634,426,Workorder,Can you determine if there are any causal relationships between KPI anomalies to gain a deeper understanding of their severity and interdependencies?,Decision Support,False,"The LLM ReAct identifies causal relationships between anomalies across KPIs to understand system-wide impact and severity. Two causal linkages were identified between anomalies across KPIs: one related to Misalignment under Structural and Mechanical Failures and another to Insufficient Insulation under Energy Efficiency. Each issue occurred once, suggesting distinct yet potentially impactful contributors to system performance degradation.",prescriptive,Equipment,Source: Maintenance operations; Non-deterministic query allowing multiple valid responses; Category: Decision Support,paraphrase,,,2024-11-27T12:38:00
